      <h1 class='title'>Inpatient Treatment</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c98WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_98ws' title='Col. 98WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c98WS' name='column_98ws' href='#column_98ws' rel='bookmark'>98WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05193'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_502'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-simon-burns' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_502' title='Link to this speech by Mr Simon Burns' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-simon-burns" title="Mr Simon Burns">Mr. Burns</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05193">To ask the Secretary of State for Health how many people are waiting for inpatient hospital treatment in the Mid-Essex Hospital Trust area. [132931]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05194'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_503'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-stephen-ladyman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_503' title='Link to this speech by Dr Stephen Ladyman' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-stephen-ladyman" title="Dr Stephen Ladyman">Dr. Ladyman</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05194"> <span class="italic">[holding answer 23 October 2003]:</span> The number of patients waiting for elective inpatient admission at Mid Essex Hospital Services National Health Service Trust was 8,120 at 31 August 2003.</p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05195"><span class="italic">Source:</span></p><p id="S6CV0412P0-05196">Department of Health Form KH07.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
